        <comment xml:lang="en">100% of the clinker is transported  by road. The transportation data by road is calculated from data from 1 clinker producing plant in TN and the transportation distances to the grinding facilities (and/or cement plant).  The 153,111 km transportation distance has been derived from primary data collection for one plant that produces 15% of the total yearly clinker production in TN.</comment>
